@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title Abstractie: aplicatie peste HTTP

package "Client" {
  rectangle "Aplicatie client" as AC
  rectangle "HTTP client" as HC
  AC -down-> HC
}

package "Server" {
  rectangle "HTTP server" as HS
  rectangle "Aplicatie server\n(logica)" as AS
  HS -down-> AS
}

HC --> HS : HTTP request/response

note bottom
  Aplicatia foloseste HTTP ca mecanism de transport logic.
  Straturile de sub aplicatie sunt ascunse de abstractie.
end note
@enduml